hopla set-hopla - group command for setting hopla related authorization and configuration

For more help use `hopla --help set-hopla {SUB_COMMAND}`

syntax:
    hopla [global_options] set-hopla {SUB_COMMAND}...

SUPPORTED SUB COMMANDS:
    hopla set-hopla credentials   - attain rights to talk to the habitica API
    hopla set-hopla config        - configure hopla settings

